@haydn70ac:

Surprisingly, there actually IS a DC comics superhero named Supergirl -- it's not a fake.  Her name is Kara Zor-El, and she's Clark Kent's/Kal-El's long lost Kryptonian cousin.  She has her own comic book and even an '80s movie starring Helen Slater, and the character was also featured on TV's Smallville.  God damn, I'm such a nerd....

